894
01:12:02,902 --> 01:12:04,063
Fuck!

895
01:12:06,197 --> 01:12:07,562
Shit.

896
01:13:00,251 --> 01:13:03,334
<i>Expedition Team, do you read me?
This is</i> Covenant.

897
01:13:04,297 --> 01:13:05,628
