919
01:13:55,097 --> 01:13:56,929
Upworth 1-4-8-9-2.

920
01:13:57,099 --> 01:13:58,885
<i>Unlocking command override ports.</i>

921
01:13:59,060 --> 01:14:01,848
Come on, Ricks, smile.
This shit should be fun.

922
01:14:15,785 --> 01:14:17,696
Where did Rosenthal go? I told...

923
01:14:18,079 --> 01:14:18,944
I'll find her.

924
01:14:19,121 --> 01:14:22,364
No, I'll go. I need to think...

925
01:14:22,541 --> 01:14:24,703
and gather my stray flock.

926
01:15:16,095 --> 01:15:17,130
Move.

927
01:15:18,180 --> 01:15:19,636
Don't shoot.

928
01:15:20,182 --> 01:15:22,469
Don't shoot.

929
01:15:24,437 --> 01:15:26,178
Communication, Captain.

930
01:15:31,944 --> 01:15:34,276
Breathe on the nostrils of a horse...

931
01:15:34,864 --> 01:15:36,946
and he'll be yours for life.

932
01:15:37,324 --> 01:15:39,281
But you have to get close.

933
01:15:40,036 --> 01:15:42,118
You have to earn its respect.

934
01:15:43,330 --> 01:15:44,786
No!

935
01:15:44,957 --> 01:15:46,447
Out of the way! Move!

936
01:15:54,967 --> 01:15:56,457
How could you?

937
01:15:56,844 --> 01:15:58,710
It trusted me.

938
01:16:10,024 --> 01:16:13,983
David, I met the devil
when I was a child...

939
01:16:14,820 --> 01:16:16,811
and I've never forgotten him.

940
01:16:17,490 --> 01:16:21,950
80, David, you're gonna tell me
exactly what's going on...

941
01:16:23,746 --> 01:16:25,828
or I am going to seriously...

942
01:16:25,998 --> 01:16:28,990
fuck up your perfect composure.

943
01:16:30,586 --> 01:16:31,701
As you wish, Captain.

944
01:16:33,005 --> 01:16:34,370
This way.

945
01:16:39,678 --> 01:16:41,339
<i>It's good to hear your voice, Tee.</i>

946
01:16:41,514 --> 01:16:42,379
<i>How long?</i>

947
01:16:42,556 --> 01:16:44,968
Mother is saying the storm is going to
