- Yeah.

959
01:17:09,708 --> 01:17:11,415
<i>We'll be there, Ground Team.</i>

960
01:17:11,585 --> 01:17:13,952
Great. Thanks, Tee.

961
01:17:14,130 --> 01:17:16,212
<i>Hey, Daniels, is Faris around?</i>

962
01:17:16,382 --> 01:17:18,464
<i>I'd like to say a quick hello
to my lady, if that's possible.</i>

963
01:17:20,803 --> 01:17:23,465
<i>Can you switch to a private channel?</i>

964
01:17:23,639 --> 01:17:25,221
<i>Let me know when you're alone.</i>

965
01:17:32,439 --> 01:17:33,725
