966
01:17:37,695 --> 01:17:39,277
<i>Maggie's gone.</i>

967
01:17:42,241 --> 01:17:44,278
<i>I'm so sorry, Tee.</i>

968
01:17:45,870 --> 01:17:49,909
<i>We tried to help her,
but we didn't make it.</i>

969
01:17:55,671 --> 01:17:56,661
Tee?

970
01:18:00,509 --> 01:18:01,795
Copy.

971
01:18:01,969 --> 01:18:03,380
<i>I'm so sorry.</i>

972
