I suppose.

974
01:18:20,112 --> 01:18:22,774
The pathogen took so many forms...

975
01:18:22,948 --> 01:18:24,655
and was extremely mutable.

976
01:18:25,743 --> 01:18:28,326
Fiendishly inventive, in fact.

977
01:18:28,495 --> 01:18:30,281
