are these gorgeous beasts.

982
01:18:43,469 --> 01:18:44,880
Patience is everything.

983
01:18:46,555 --> 01:18:49,297
From the eggs came these parasites...

984
01:18:50,100 --> 01:18:52,467
shock troops of the genetic assault.

985
01:18:53,479 --> 01:18:56,813
Waiting for a host, entering the host...

986
01:18:57,399 --> 01:18:59,106
rewriting the DNA...

987
01:19:00,486 --> 01:19:01,942
and ultimately...

988
01:19:03,030 --> 01:19:03,986
producing...

989
01:19:06,200 --> 01:19:07,782
these enviable unions.

990
01:19:08,911 --> 01:19:10,902
My beautiful bestiary.

991
01:19:12,248 --> 01:19:15,536
Soon enough, I began a bit
of genetic experimentation of my own.

992
01:19:16,210 --> 01:19:17,621
Some crossbreeding, hybridizing...

993
01:19:17,795 --> 01:19:19,035
what have you.

994
01:19:19,213 --> 01:19:21,079
You engineered these, David?

995
01:19:21,257 --> 01:19:24,420
Idle hands are
the devil's workshop, Captain.

996
01:19:25,261 --> 01:19:26,296
Come.

997
01:19:26,971 --> 01:19:29,212
This is what I wanted to show you.

998
01:19:30,516 --> 01:19:31,756
My successes.

999
01:19:34,895 --> 01:19:36,181
You see, Captain...

1000
01:19:36,480 --> 01:19:38,016
