1002
01:19:57,334 --> 01:19:58,699
Are they alive?

1003
01:20:01,422 --> 01:20:03,163
Waiting, really.

1004
01:20:04,008 --> 01:20:05,498
For what?

1005
01:20:08,846 --> 01:20:10,302
What are they waiting for, David?

1006
01:20:11,557 --> 01:20:12,638
Mother.

1007
01:20:20,858 --> 01:20:23,691
Perfectly safe, I assure you.

1008
01:20:33,954 --> 01:20:35,490
Take a look.

1009
01:20:36,582 --> 01:20:37,788
Something to see.

1010
01:21:10,616 --> 01:21:12,357
<i>Rosenthal, come in.</i>

1011
01:21:14,244 --> 01:21:15,826
<i>Rosie, report.</i>

1012
01:21:20,751 --> 01:21:22,082
<i>Rosie?</i>

1013
01:21:24,088 --> 01:21:25,874
<i>Cole, where are you?</i>

1014
01:21:26,548 --> 01:21:28,038
I found her, Sarge.

1015
01:21:32,096 --> 01:21:34,383
Fuck!
Okay, prep the gear.

1016
01:21:34,932 --> 01:21:36,263
We gotta get out of here.

1017
01:21:36,433 --> 01:21:37,764
Where the fuck is the captain?

1018
01:21:37,935 --> 01:21:39,096
He's not answering his radio.

1019
01:21:39,478 --> 01:21:40,434
Listen to me.

1020
01:21:40,604 --> 01:21:44,313
I'm gonna contact the ship,
get them to launch as soon as they can.

1021
