1135
01:33:23,389 --> 01:33:25,847
<i>Yeah, I can hear you.
Send me your location.</i>

1136
01:33:27,727 --> 01:33:29,343
Sending the beacon now.

1137
01:33:51,709 --> 01:33:53,199
<i>Tee, do you have a visual?</i>

1138
01:33:53,378 --> 01:33:55,870
Okay, I see your beacon.

1139
01:33:56,047 --> 01:33:57,378
I'm coming in.

1140
01:34:01,052 --> 01:34:02,383
Get out of here.

1141
01:34:08,226 --> 01:34:09,808
<i>I'm comin' in hot!</i>

1142
01:34:28,246 --> 01:34:30,078
Hurry! I can't hold this for long.

1143
01:34:40,091 --> 01:34:41,252
Open the door, Tee.

1144
01:34:44,262 --> 01:34:45,297
Get in.

1145
