Where's David?

1146
01:34:50,185 --> 01:34:51,266
Expired.

1147
01:34:55,273 --> 01:34:56,855
Hey! We got company!

1148
01:34:57,025 --> 01:34:58,607
- What?
- We got company!

1149
01:34:58,776 --> 01:34:59,937
On the underside of the ship.

1150
01:35:00,111 --> 01:35:00,976
Shit!

1151
01:35:01,946 --> 01:35:03,436
Motherfucker!

1152
01:35:06,201 --> 01:35:07,566
Open the door.

1153
01:35:16,336 --> 01:35:17,326
Give me a shot.

1154
01:35:17,503 --> 01:35:18,618
Give me a shot.

1155
01:35:28,348 --> 01:35:30,806
Forward engine, starboard side.

1156
01:35:30,975 --> 01:35:32,761
I'm gonna try and torch the fucker.

1157
01:35:38,775 --> 01:35:39,765
Shit! I can't get it!

1158
01:35:40,944 --> 01:35:42,434
Hold tight! Hold tight!

1159
01:35:42,612 --> 01:35:43,818
I'm starting my climb.

1160
01:35:55,333 --> 01:35:56,323
Fuck!

1161
01:36:00,588 --> 01:36:01,669
Hold on!

1162
01:36:15,270 --> 01:36:17,136
Damn it! Shit!

1163
01:36:17,313 --> 01:36:18,178
Bring me up.

1164
01:36:28,199 --> 01:36:29,485
Holy shit!

1165
01:36:30,076 --> 01:36:31,566
I got eyes on it.

1166
01:36:31,744 --> 01:36:33,985
It's right fucking in front of me.

1167
01:36:34,831 --> 01:36:36,947
Tee, give me the axe.

1168
01:36:37,125 --> 01:36:38,240
Throw her the axe!

1169
01:36:44,215 --> 01:36:45,330
Release the crane.

1170
01:36:46,217 --> 01:36:47,503
I can't do that.

1171
01:36:47,677 --> 01:36:48,883
It'll unbalance us.

1172
01:36:49,053 --> 01:36:50,384
Just do it.

1173
01:36:50,555 --> 01:36:51,465
Shit!

1174
01:37:14,370 --> 01:37:15,485
Hold tight!

1175
01:37:15,663 --> 01:37:16,744
<i>Compensating!</i>

1176
01:37:47,445 --> 01:37:48,185
Shit!

1177
01:37:51,824 --> 01:37:52,655
Damn it!

1178
01:37:59,332 --> 01:38:01,539
Shit! Hold on!

1179
01:38:02,877 --> 01:38:04,208
<i>Bring me up, Tee.</i>

1180
01:38:04,379 --> 01:38:05,369
Copy.

1181
01:38:25,525 --> 01:38:26,515
How is it?

1182
01:38:26,692 --> 01:38:27,853
It's fine.

1183
01:38:40,665 --> 01:38:41,450
Walter!

1184
01:38:41,624 --> 01:38:44,412
Get her inside.
We're getting out of here.

1185
01:39:02,478 --> 01:39:03,388
Door!

1186
01:39:04,480 --> 01:39:05,970
Well done, Tee.

1187
01:39:06,524 --> 01:39:08,185
Walk in the park.

1188
01:39:24,250 --> 01:39:26,867
I gave him a pretty heavy sedative.

1189
01:39:28,129 --> 01:39:30,370
Jesus. Poor Lope.

1190
01:39:31,466 --> 01:39:33,503
He looks like Phantom of the Opera.

1191
01:39:34,135 --> 01:39:36,046
I didn't peg you for a musical fan.

1192
01:39:36,220 --> 01:39:37,460
That's a musical?

1193
01:39:39,640 --> 01:39:42,473
I'm just a medic.
He's gonna need reconstructive surgery...

1194
01:39:42,643 --> 01:39:44,008
by a real doctor.

1195
01:40:08,252 --> 01:40:09,742
Let me do that.

1196
01:40:15,426 --> 01:40:16,416
Thank you.

1197
01:40:20,431 --> 01:40:22,718
Thank you for saving my life.

1198
01:40:25,186 --> 01:40:26,176
Again.

1199
01:40:29,565 --> 01:40:30,851
It's my duty.

1200
01:40:58,302 --> 01:40:59,292
Yeah.

1201
01:41:02,390 --> 01:41:03,380
Evening.

1202
01:41:04,225 --> 01:41:05,681
- You look good.
- What?

1203
01:41:06,269 --> 01:41:07,851
Yeah, gorgeous.

1204
01:41:10,273 --> 01:41:12,605
I took Mother offline.

1205
01:41:12,775 --> 01:41:14,436
She needs a full diagnostic.

1206
01:41:14,610 --> 01:41:17,648
She got the shit beat out of her
in that storm, a lot of EM damage.

1207
01:41:18,239 --> 01:41:20,276
She will be back online at eight bells.

1208
01:41:20,950 --> 01:41:22,611
Right. Thanks, Tee.

1209
01:41:25,997 --> 01:41:28,659
Does this mean
I have to call you Captain now?

1210
01:41:28,833 --> 01:41:30,164
Fuck yes.

1211
01:42:04,493 --> 01:42:05,858
<i>Attention.</i>

1212
01:42:06,037 --> 01:42:09,371
<i>Captain Daniels,
please report to the Med Bay.</i>

1213
01:42:13,586 --> 01:42:15,202
<i>Attention.</i>

1214
01:42:15,379 --> 01:42:18,838
<i>Captain Daniels,
please report to the Med Bay.</i>

1215
01:42:22,303 --> 01:42:23,543
Why, Mother?

1216
01:42:23,721 --> 01:42:27,464
<i>There is an unidentified life form
on the ship.</i>

1217
01:42:33,773 --> 01:42:35,184
<i>Attention.</i>

1218
01:42:35,358 --> 01:42:39,067
<i>Captain Daniels, please report
to the Med Bay.</i>

1219
01:42:39,487 --> 01:42:40,477
<i>Repeat.</i>

1220
01:42:40,655 --> 01:42:44,114
<i>Captain Daniels, please report
to the Med Bay.</i>

1221
01:42:51,916 --> 01:42:52,906
Jesus.

1222
01:42:53,209 --> 01:42:54,290
Oh, my God.

1223
01:42:57,213 --> 01:42:58,248
Walter.

1224
01:42:59,298 --> 01:43:01,039
Location of unidentified life form.

1225
01:43:02,218 --> 01:43:03,754
Any movement at all?

1226
01:43:07,181 --> 01:43:08,171
Walter!

1227
01:43:09,016 --> 01:43:10,006
<i>Stand by.</i>

1228
01:43:13,979 --> 01:43:15,561
There it is.

1229
01:43:15,731 --> 01:43:17,938
B-Deck between hex 3 and 4.

1230
01:43:18,109 --> 01:43:19,599
<i>Heading for crew quarters.</i>

1231
01:43:20,027 --> 01:43:21,734
<i>Is anyone down there?</i>

1232
01:43:21,904 --> 01:43:22,939
Ricks and Upworth.

1233
01:43:23,114 --> 01:43:25,196
Shit. We're on our way.

1234
01:43:25,366 --> 01:43:27,277
Walter! Sound the alarm!

1235
01:43:27,451 --> 01:43:28,441
Warn them!

1236
01:43:29,036 --> 01:43:30,276
<i>Attention.</i>

1237
01:43:30,454 --> 01:43:32,320
<i>Ricks and Upworth...</i>

1238
01:43:32,498 --> 01:43:34,990
<i>evacuate crew quarters immediately.</i>

1239
01:44:15,916 --> 01:44:16,826
No!

1240
01:44:23,174 --> 01:44:24,164
No!

1241
01:44:31,557 --> 01:44:32,547
Seal B-39.

1242
01:44:34,226 --> 01:44:36,342
<i>8-39 closed.</i>

1243
01:45:07,384 --> 01:45:08,374
Walter.

1244
01:45:09,720 --> 01:45:11,711
- Where is it?
- Daniels.

1245
01:45:12,765 --> 01:45:13,596
This way.

1246
01:45:22,149 --> 01:45:24,390
Tee, let's choose our ground.

1247
01:45:24,568 --> 01:45:25,933
We'll bring it to us.

1248
01:45:26,111 --> 01:45:27,146
Where?

1249
01:45:28,447 --> 01:45:29,437
My turf.

1250
01:45:30,074 --> 01:45:33,738
<i>Walter, seal all doors behind us
and keep hatch to Level-C open.</i>

1251
01:45:33,994 --> 01:45:35,234
Understood.

1252
01:45:38,249 --> 01:45:40,115
<i>B-44 closed.</i>

1253
01:45:44,964 --> 01:45:47,126
<i>B-46 closed.</i>

1254
01:45:48,092 --> 01:45:50,254
<i>B-47, B-45, and B-43 closed.</i>

1255
01:45:50,427 --> 01:45:52,168
<i>B-9 closed.</i>

1256
01:45:52,346 --> 01:45:55,088
<i>B-6 and B-5 closed.</i>

1257
01:45:59,770 --> 01:46:01,101
<i>Okay, Walter, where is it?</i>

1258
01:46:03,607 --> 01:46:05,939
It's on B-Deck. Starboard side...

1259
01:46:06,110 --> 01:46:07,350
descending into C-Level.

1260
01:46:08,112 --> 01:46:09,102
<i>K-13.</i>

1261
01:46:23,002 --> 01:46:24,117
Hey, Tee.

1262
01:46:24,795 --> 01:46:26,377
Come on. Walter?

1263
01:46:27,131 --> 01:46:28,667
Open starboard C-64...

1264
01:46:28,841 --> 01:46:30,832
<i>and clear his path to the Terraforming Bay.</i>

1265
01:46:31,010 --> 01:46:32,216
Understood.

1266
01:46:38,976 --> 01:46:42,719
Seal C-61, open airlock 17.
We're going in.

1267
01:46:52,990 --> 01:46:54,480
K-12 secured.

1268
01:46:57,661 --> 01:47:00,494
Okay. Keep him in Knuckle-12
till my say.

1269
01:47:10,549 --> 01:47:12,916
<i>Tee, this is what we're gonna do.</i>

1270
01:47:13,093 --> 01:47:15,334
<i>I'M lure it into the truck,
lock it in the cab...</i>

1271
01:47:15,512 --> 01:47:18,595
<i>and when I say when,
you blow this fucker into space.</i>

1272
01:47:18,766 --> 01:47:19,722
<i>Understood.</i>

1273
01:47:19,892 --> 01:47:21,724
<i>Okay, Walter. We're ready.</i>

1274
01:47:21,894 --> 01:47:23,851
Open door to Terraforming Bay.

1275
01:47:24,021 --> 01:47:25,352
<i>Opening airlock now.</i>

1276
01:47:36,867 --> 01:47:38,073
Walter...

1277
01:47:38,243 --> 01:47:39,904
move him into airlock 18.

1278
01:47:46,210 --> 01:47:48,042
Don't shoot, if you can avoid it.

1279
01:47:48,212 --> 01:47:50,499
Its blood will eat through the hull.

1280
01:47:50,673 --> 01:47:51,663
Great.

1281
01:47:52,174 --> 01:47:53,209
I'm in position.

1282
01:47:54,677 --> 01:47:57,419
Walter, open door to Terraforming Bay.

1283
01:48:00,557 --> 01:48:02,343
<i>It's all yours.</i>

1284
01:48:02,518 --> 01:48:04,885
Remember, release when I say.

1285
01:48:05,229 --> 01:48:06,435
Understood.

1286
01:48:12,569 --> 01:48:14,025
Let's kill this fucker.

1287
01:48:19,910 --> 01:48:21,025
Fuck!

1288
01:48:44,435 --> 01:48:46,142
I got you, you son of a bitch!

1289
01:48:51,817 --> 01:48:54,980
<i>Tennessee, open the doors, now!</i>

1290
01:48:57,281 --> 01:49:00,239
<i>Warning.
Atmospheric decompression in progress.</i>

1291
01:49:01,410 --> 01:49:03,947
<i>Warning.
Atmospheric decompression in progress.</i>

1292
01:49:24,433 --> 01:49:26,094
<i>It's jammed!
Release the second truck!</i>

1293
01:49:26,268 --> 01:49:27,258
You got it!

1294
01:49:28,604 --> 01:49:29,935
Here it comes!

1295
01:49:54,963 --> 01:49:56,545
Daniels! Heads up!

1296
01:50:17,361 --> 01:50:18,692
Daniels!

1297
01:50:36,421 --> 01:50:39,004
You wanna give a girl a hand?

1298
01:51:04,366 --> 01:51:05,856
See you soon.

1299
01:51:16,003 --> 01:51:18,040
You're next, Captain.

1300
01:51:36,190 --> 01:51:39,524
When you wake up, we'll be at Origae-6.

1301
01:51:42,070 --> 01:51:44,277
What do you think it's gonna be like?

1302
01:51:47,034 --> 01:51:49,071
I think if we are kind...

1303
01:51:50,370 --> 01:51:52,031
it will be a kind world.

1304
01:51:54,291 --> 01:51:56,032
I hope you're right.

1305
01:51:58,128 --> 01:51:59,789
Sleep well.

1306
01:52:07,471 --> 01:52:08,461
Walter.

1307
01:52:11,475 --> 01:52:15,639
When we get there,
will you help me build my cabin?

1308
01:52:20,651 --> 01:52:22,392
The cabin on the lake.

1309
01:52:28,075 --> 01:52:29,236
David?

1310
01:52:34,414 --> 01:52:35,654
No...

1311
01:52:36,166 --> 01:52:36,997
No!

1312
01:52:46,093 --> 01:52:48,460
Don't let the bedbugs bite.

1313
01:52:51,598 --> 01:52:53,339
I'll tuck in the children.

1314
01:53:05,279 --> 01:53:09,273
Use security code
David 73694-B.

1315
01:53:11,368 --> 01:53:13,655
<i>Welcome. How may I help you?</i>

1316
01:53:14,955 --> 01:53:16,662
How about some music, Mother?

1317
01:53:16,832 --> 01:53:18,118
<i>Selection?</i>

1318
01:53:18,292 --> 01:53:22,206
Richard Wagner. <i>Das Rheingold,</i> Act Two.

1319
01:53:23,880 --> 01:53:27,794
<i>The Entry of the Gods into Valhalla.</i>

1320
01:53:27,968 --> 01:53:30,881
<i>Yes, David. As you wish.</i>

1321
01:54:58,642 --> 01:55:01,725
<i>This is colony ship</i> Covenant, <i>reporting.</i>

1322
01:55:01,895 --> 01:55:04,478
<i>All crew members
apart from Daniels and Tennessee...</i>

1323
01:55:04,648 --> 01:55:07,060
<i>tragically perished
in a solar flare incident.</i>

1324
01:55:07,818 --> 01:55:11,482
<i>All colonists in hypersleep remain intact
and undisturbed.</i>

1325
01:55:12,322 --> 01:55:14,279
<i>On course for Origae-6.</i>

1326
01:55:15,117 --> 01:55:17,074
<i>Hopefully this transmission will reach
the network...</i>

1327
01:55:17,244 --> 01:55:19,611
<i>and be relayed in 1.36 years.</i>

1328
01:55:20,497 --> 01:55:22,079
<i>This is Waiter, signing off.</i>

1329
01:55:22,249 --> 01:55:25,992
<i>Security code, 31564-F.</i>

